        <item>
          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>Faith and Fairness Act of 2014 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to define "minister of the gospel" for purposes of the tax exclusion of the rental value of a home or rental allowance provided to such minister&nbsp;to include any duly recognized official of a religious, spiritual, moral, or ethical organization (whether theistic or not). </p>]]></text>
          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2014-06-19T18:22:55Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
